{"type":"message","id":"12a48073","parentId":"85a93eeb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:43:31.043Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gw3qzfv7s05a_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 2311\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='# Pending\n\n## Promises Made\n(N' file='state/goals.md' new_len=491\r\n[mutation proposed] state/goals.md\r\n[master 2ba6f7a] pulse: 2026-03-24 144318\n 6 files changed, 138 insertions(+), 83 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 144318.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 144318.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 144141.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 144318 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed a critical insight: constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.00) are metaprogramming contamination, not true causal patterns. The next step is testing the hybrid scoring formula that should distinguish these from genuine research trajectory tokens.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 2311\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='# Pending\n\n## Promises Made\n(N' file='state/goals.md' new_len=491\r\n[mutation proposed] state/goals.md\r\n[master 2ba6f7a] pulse: 2026-03-24 144318\n 6 files changed, 138 insertions(+), 83 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 144318.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 144318.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 144141.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 144318 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed a critical insight: constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.00) are metaprogramming contamination, not true causal patterns. The next step is testing the hybrid scoring formula that should distinguish these from genuine research trajectory tokens.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pu